headline: Assessing HCA Healthcare After a 68% Rally and Strong Cash Flow Outlook in 2025
summary: If you are wondering whether HCA Healthcare is still a smart buy after such a big run up, or if you are late to the party, this breakdown is for you. Despite a slight pullback of around 3.0% over the last week, the stock is still up 8.8% over 30 days and 68.0% year to date, with a 54.2% gain over the past year and 227.7% over five years.
